{"tid":2164382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍連叫雞都要節儉，制止浪費","createTime":"2020-08-19T07:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T07:25:25.000Z","uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c32d53be23299bf0723a92e03c6cf3e1d7bef0a3","tid":2164382,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"習近平日前號召制止中國人的浪費行為，啟動節儉養德全民節約社會風尚。大陸有餐廳響應，開始對客人有先磅重，後叫餸之要求，需顧客依照自己的體重按食物熱量點餐。<br />\n<br />\n先不討論為何鼓吹肥人吃更多東西是否反智，政府的確有意承上起下執行運動，除了要市民行「N-1點餐模式」，10位進餐客人只能點9人份量的菜，政府內部亦切實遏制公務支出和公款消費中的浪費，網流傳解放軍上年的聚會已開始實行「N/2點女模式」，10個解放軍，只能點5位小姐，同時實踐「不舉，就不叫女」的清廉節儉美德。<br />\n<br />\n全國人民制止浪費絕不是天方夜譚，近代史上中國曾經就有全國響應的節儉運動，更有超過至少四千萬人不惜以生命去防止食物被浪費，史稱「大躍進」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/117873203_3266103310113932_3001014563869209043_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=WGDe2yKI_fYAX_3Lhjt&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=de64fda3a2dc83d3dc8d9e4885b026ae&amp;oe=5F640285\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F117873203_3266103310113932_3001014563869209043_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DWGDe2yKI_fYAX_3Lhjt%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dde64fda3a2dc83d3dc8d9e4885b026ae%26oe%3D5F640285&h=6ac91c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nby 向西<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/xxharuki/photos/a.353973134660312/3266103306780599/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fxxharuki%2Fphotos%2Fa.353973134660312%2F3266103306780599%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=86570a3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/xxharuki/photos/a.353973134660312/3266103306780599/</a>"}]}